DEVICEDEF
 testdoor         // label, name of device
 90.0 rotatez 90.0 rotatex
push  0.0 3.0 0.0 copynvals 1.0 0.2 2.3 scalexyz 3.0 3.0 0.0 copynvals 0.0 0.0 1.0 setcolor 1.0 drawcube pop // front half of door (user specified color)
push  0.0 3.0 0.0 copynvals 1.0 0.2 2.3 scalexyz 0.0 0.0 1.0 setcolor 0.0 1.0 0.0 translate 1.0 drawcube pop // back half of door (blue)
